Dependencies:
    parted
    udisks
    kde 4.6.1
    python 2.7
    qt 4.7.1

Installation:
    sudo python setup.py install

Running:
    Debug mode:
        xhost+
        sudo su -
        quickformat

    Normal mode:
        run from KDE programs menu
